snippet.title: Simply Not Logical
snippet.description:
Holo, I'm Cristine, that 30-something nail lady. I also do things that are simply not logical.

Join me 🔴LIVE🔴 for SIMPLY STREAM on this channel every: 
WEDNESDAY at 5PM ET / 2PM PT
SATURDAY at 11AM ET / 8AM PT

Main channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/simplynailogical
Podcast: https://www.youtube.com/simplypodlogical
Holo Taco (my nail polish brand): https://www.youtube.com/holotaco

Instagram: @simplynailogical
My cats' Instagrams: @menchiethecat @zylerthecat
Twitter: @nailogical
Snapchat: simplynailogica (no "L"!)
Facebook: Simply Nailogical
TikTok: @simplynailogical
Discord: http://discord.gg/simplynailogical
